<sect1 id="IsValidTime">
  <title>IsValidTime</title>

  <para><emphasis role="bold">STD.Date.IsValidTime<indexterm>
      <primary>STD.Date.IsValidTime</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>Date.IsValidTime</primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary>IsValidTime</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis> <emphasis>time</emphasis> <emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
    <tgroup cols="2">
      <colspec colwidth="80.50pt"/>

      <colspec/>

      <tbody>
        <row>
          <entry><emphasis>time</emphasis></entry>

          <entry>Um valor de hora no formato Time_t.</entry>
        </row>

        <row>
          <entry>Return:</entry>

          <entry>IsValidTime retorna um valor BOOLEAN</entry>
        </row>
      </tbody>
    </tgroup>
  </informaltable>

  <para>A <emphasis role="bold"/> função IsValidDate retorna TRUE se a hora é
  válida, verificando cada um dos componentes individuais (horas, minutos e
  segundos).</para>

  <para>Exemplo:</para>

  <programlisting format="linespecific">IMPORT STD;
d1 := 19631122;
d2 := 19990230;  
firstTest := STD.Date.IsValidDate(d1);  //d1 is valid
secondTest := STD.Date.IsValidDate(d2); //d2 is not valid
</programlisting>

  <para/>
</sect1>
